Package: choicer
Title: Discrete Choice Models for Economists by Economists
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Fernando", "Cordeiro", , "fernandolpcordeiro@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: `choicer` aims to offer a series of choice model implementations with a focus on economic applications.
    Computationally intensive likelihood functions are implemented in C++ and are exported to be called by any solver.
